ISLAMABAD, Oct 9 (APP):National Assembly Speaker Sardar Ayaz Sadiq on Wednesday condemned the assassination attack on provincial Parliamentary secretary Punjab Chaudary Naeem Ijaz.
In a statement, the Speaker extended well wishes for the Member Punjab Assembly safety and added that accused involved in the attempt of murder attack should be brought to justice.
